title: Ceiling Border, 1875–1906
creditline: Museum purchase from Smithsonian Institution Collections Acquisition Program and Sarah Cooper-Hewitt Funds
description:
Wallpaper roll. 
Ceiling medallion, with large circular medallion having four corners, containing pink and blue flowers. Two square medallions between circles. Printed on tan ground.
